697}, {"id": 11616, "content": "Mac，Mac，超级cool的办公环境！！舒服的休闲区，绿化绿化，最好像森林一样！！水果，零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184325}, {"id": 12385, "content": "可爱的老板娘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 192266}, {"id": 11623, "content": "一分钟100块", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179883}, {"id": 11624, "content": "零食，零食，零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147022}, {"id": 13420, "content": "加班费", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 206898}, {"id": 12400, "content": "奇异的空间布置 让人觉得在魔幻城堡 超级舒适", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 192872}, {"id": 11646, "content": "萌妹纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72816}, {"id": 16767, "content": "办公室的环境舒适、办公室的氛围同事相处和谐轻松，不勾心斗角，个个工作积极上进，有朝气，感觉不仅是好的团体更让人觉得是个温馨的大家庭。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 242160}, {"id": 11136, "content": "沙发，很多很多沙发", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 11137, "content": "我司的猫总", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 18305, "content": "wifi", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256049}, {"id": 11138, "content": "我妈，一回家就问我为啥还没对象…", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 11139, "content": "我对象，一回家就让我煮饭洗碗…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 11657, "content": "猫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 12434, "content": "聊的好的同事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190634}, {"id": 11672, "content": "酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175931}, {"id": 11679, "content": "好领导好同事", 